64 signals in array of size: 16 12 (indicated in the top)
The leading 9 entries refer to signals from which the
standard 12-leads are derived.Order: V1-V6, VR, VL, VF
lead 48 appoximates VF since VF was not recorded separately.
If WCT data are used: VF=-(VL+VR)

